To start the server application, 44444 and 55555 ports should be open in the firewall.
For ubuntu, the commands are
$ ufw allow 44444
$ ufw allow 55555
$ javac TCPServer.java
$ java TCPServer

After last command the server will wait client devices to connect, 
if cannot disable firewall and run the program again 

$ ufw disable
$ java TCPServer
